l/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nset rb唔緊要 次次set完就聚人 又密 要走都冇位走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T21:17:20.000Z","msg":"都真 be water真係好有用<br />\n5.24班狗除咗銅鑼灣嗰啲都唔知點好<br />\n我地一路係咁變 佢地就一路部署唔到"},{"pid":"119714412a62ba057812e680e204a9ec34e97466","tid":2035034,"uid":199898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T21:22:03.000Z","msg":"同埋發夢有一次見過喺漆咸道成地都係碎磚<br />\n應該係想整rb 但所有人一路向前行唔理啲磚<br />\n根本無諗過如果嗰時班狗一野衝過嚟<br />\n成班真係會跑唔到 會仆曬喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足們見到呢啲可唔可以一係唔好推前過個rb<br />\n一係就連埋啲rb一齊推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1dc173bb564b3eae2e3179351488917d6bcf47","tid":2035034,"uid":60410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T21:24:34.000Z","msg":"轉場要快"},{"pid":"db1d561a45302428324d411aca4bdbdc38ea50de","tid":2035034,"uid":199898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad1dc173bb564b3eae2e3179351488917d6bcf47","tid":2035034,"uid":60410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T21:24:34.000Z","msg":"轉場要快"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T21:29:09.000Z","msg":"轉場快之餘 轉去邊都好重要<br />\n例如有兩批人 一批喺銅鑼灣 一批喺灣仔<br />\n兩邊見無狗就可以出嚟 有狗就好縮<br />\n不過根據過往經驗 <br />\n班狗係會集中搞完一批先 之後先搞另一區"},{"pid":"29fab20a582dbe1aa02160e2c0f8413e3190583a","tid":2035034,"uid":199898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T21:52:26.000Z","msg":"push"}]}